naointerface.main

Annotation Type NoBodyPart


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
@interface NoBodyPart
    This annotation is written to mark fields in the utility class naointerface.main.BodyParts that are no BodyParts.
    This is important so that reflective methods work correctly.
    Author:
    Nelli Welker, Etienne Onasch
